data.description: Beautiful 4 Bedroom, 2.5 Bath home on a nicely landscaped 1-acre parcel in a highly desirable established community. Close to shopping and town. Wonderful floorplan that flows from the entry to either the formal living room or the large family room that includes vaulted ceiling, fireplace, open wood staircase, plenty of windows and deck access. Modern brand new kitchen with pantry, Quartz countertop and ceramic farmhouse sink.  Includes a combined dining area with fireplace and sliding glass doors to large deck with gas grilling area.  Primary bedroom with customized walk-in closet and large bath with Jacuzzi tub. Hardwood floors throughout the main level. The open stairway leads up to 3 more bedrooms, a full bath and a large bonus room plus an attic for storage.  Also features good-sized Laundry room, 2 car garage, paved driveway/ parking area and is adjacent to the common area.
